---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTAButton from '../components/CTAButton.astro';
import OtherInstructors from '../components/OtherInstructors.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="George Digweed MBE - 31-Time World Champion"
  description="Learn from George Digweed MBE, widely considered the greatest clay shooter of all time. 31+ World Championships, Guinness World Record holder, and MBE recipient."
>
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="container-max">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1 class="hero-title">
            George <span class="text-accent">Digweed MBE</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">
            The Greatest Clay Shooter of All Time
          </p>
          
          <!-- Stats Bar -->
          <div class="stats-container">
            <div class="stats-bar">
              <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">31+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">World Titles</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-divider"></div>
              <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">35+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Years Competing</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-divider"></div>
              <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">3,000+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Students Trained</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-divider"></div>
              <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">MBE</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Royal Honor</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="hero-description">
            Learn from the undisputed legend with an unmatched record of dominance. George's revolutionary Swing-Through method has created champions worldwide.
          </p>
          
          <!-- CTA -->
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <CTAButton
              text="Master George's Method"
              href="https://digital.claytargetinstruction.com/l/products?sortKey=name&sortDirection=asc&page=1&authorId=2149776"
              variant="primary"
              size="large"
              external={true}
              trackingId="george_bio_main_cta"
              withArrow={true}
              usePulse={true}
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Hero Image -->
        <div class="hero-image-container">
          <div class="hero-image">
            <img 
              src="/assets/images/george_digweed_instructor_hero_desktop.jpg" 
              alt="George Digweed MBE - 31x World Champion Clay Target Shooter"
            />
            <div class="image-overlay"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Scroll indicator -->
    <div class="scroll-indicator">
      <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Legend's Journey Section -->
  <section class="journey-section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>The Making of a Legend</h2>
        <div class="gradient-underline"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="journey-content">
        <p class="lead-text">
          For over three decades, George Digweed has dominated clay shooting like no other athlete in any sport. His 31+ World Championships aren't just numbers—they represent a level of consistency and excellence that has redefined what's possible in competitive shooting.
        </p>
        
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <h3>Royal Recognition</h3>
          <p>
            In recognition of his unparalleled contributions to sport, Her Majesty the Queen awarded George the MBE (Member of the Order of the British Empire). This honor reflects not just his competitive achievements, but his role as a global ambassador for clay shooting.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <p>
          What separates George from other champions isn't just his trophy count—it's his revolutionary approach to the sport. His Swing-Through method, refined through millions of targets and hundreds of major championships, has become the gold standard for consistent, high-level performance.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Teaching Philosophy -->
  <section class="philosophy-section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>The Swing-Through Revolution</h2>
        <div class="gradient-underline"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="philosophy-grid">
        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/>
              <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Technical Mastery</h3>
          <p>
            George's method breaks down the most complex shots into repeatable, systematic movements. Every aspect—from gun mount to follow-through—is precisely engineered for consistency.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Mental Discipline</h3>
          <p>
            Beyond technique, George teaches the championship mindset that has kept him at the top for decades. Learn to manage pressure, maintain focus, and perform when it matters most.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Proven Results</h3>
          <p>
            George's students include national champions, world team members, and thousands of shooters who've dramatically improved their scores using his systematic approach.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Achievement Highlights -->
  <section class="achievements-section">
    <div class="container-max">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Unmatched Achievements</h2>
        <div class="gradient-underline"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="achievements-grid">
        <div class="achievement-card">
          <div class="achievement-number">31+</div>
          <h3>World Championships</h3>
          <p>More than any other shooter in history across all disciplines</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="achievement-card">
          <div class="achievement-text">MBE</div>
          <h3>Royal Honor</h3>
          <p>Awarded by Queen Elizabeth II for services to sport</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="achievement-card">
          <div class="achievement-number">35+</div>
          <h3>Years at the Top</h3>
          <p>Unmatched longevity and consistency at elite level</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="final-cta-section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2>Ready to Learn from the Greatest?</h2>
      <p class="final-cta-subtitle">
        Join thousands of shooters worldwide who are transforming their game with George's proven system. Get instant access to the exact methods that created the most successful competitive shooter in history.
      </p>
      <CTAButton 
        text="Start Learning from George Today"
        href="https://digital.claytargetinstruction.com/l/products?sortKey=name&sortDirection=asc&page=1&authorId=1233055"
        variant="primary"
        size="large"
        external={true}
        trackingId="george_bio_final_cta"
        usePulse={true}
        withArrow={true}
      />
      <p class="guarantee-text">
        Lifetime access • All devices • 30-day guarantee
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Container Styles */
  .container-max {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .container-narrow {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0A0B 0%, #1A1A1C 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .hero-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .text-accent {
    color: #FF6600;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #A0A0A0;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  /* Stats Bar */
  .stats-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .stats-bar {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,102,0,0.15), rgba(139,92,246,0.1));
    padding: 1.5rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 80px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
  
  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6600, #FF8800);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    opacity: 0.9;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 35px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.4), transparent);
  }
  
  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #F2F2F2;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  
  .hero-cta {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  /* Hero Image */
  .hero-image-container {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .hero-image {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 600px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  
  .hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: left;
  }
  
  .image-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.6), transparent);
  }
  
  /* Scroll Indicator */
  .scroll-indicator {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
    color: #FF6600;
  }
  
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-10px); }
  }
  
  /* Journey Section */
  .journey-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: #f8f8f8;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #111111;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .gradient-underline {
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF6600 0%, #FF8800 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  
  .journey-content {
    space-y: 2rem;
  }
  
  .lead-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #333333;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .journey-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #666666;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .highlight-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border-left: 4px solid #FF6600;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .highlight-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #111111;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  /* Philosophy Section */
  .philosophy-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0A0B 0%, #1A1A1C 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .philosophy-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom left, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  
  .philosophy-section h2 {
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }
  
  .philosophy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .philosophy-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  
  .philosophy-card {
    background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.4);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .philosophy-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.6);
    border-color: rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.2);
  }
  
  .card-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: #FF6600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .philosophy-card:hover .card-icon {
    background: rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.2);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
  
  .card-icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }
  
  .philosophy-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .philosophy-card p {
    color: #F2F2F2;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  
  /* Achievements Section */
  .achievements-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: #f5f5f5;
  }
  
  .achievements-section h2 {
    color: #111111;
  }
  
  .achievements-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .achievement-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .achievement-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 102, 0, 0.15);
  }
  
  .achievement-number,
  .achievement-text {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6600, #FF8800);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .achievement-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #111111;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .achievement-card p {
    color: #666666;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  
  /* Final CTA Section */
  .final-cta-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0A0B 0%, #1A1A1C 100%);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .final-cta-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 70%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  
  .final-cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  
  .final-cta-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #A0A0A0;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .guarantee-text {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #A0A0A0;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  
  /* Mobile Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    
    .hero-image {
      height: 400px;
    }
    
    .stats-bar {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .stat-item {
      flex: 1 1 auto;
      min-width: 60px;
      max-width: 80px;
    }
    
    .stat-number {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      word-break: break-word;
      hyphens: auto;
    }
    
    .stat-divider {
      display: none;
    }
    
    .philosophy-grid,
    .achievements-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .hero-cta {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
    
    .hero-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .final-cta-section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    
    .final-cta-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin: 0 0.5rem 1rem;
    }
    
    .final-cta-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 0 0.5rem 2rem;
      max-width: none;
    }
    
    .container-narrow {
      padding: 0 1rem;
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>